data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET THROUGH NO FAULT OF IT'S OWN.  Motivated Seller!  At this price this house could be used as an AirBnb or rental property.  WATERFRONT PROPERTY!! You have to see this home and property in person to fully appreciate it's beauty. This 4 bedroom 3 bath home is in a quiet neighborhood in Westlake. There are two master suites (one on the main level and one upstairs). The house was repaired and updated after Hurricane Laura. The roof was replaced in 2020. Two HVAC units (replaced in 2021) heat and cool the home.  An added bonus is the two gas fireplaces (one in the living room and one in the upstairs master suite). Although in flood zone AE, flood insurance is LESS THAN $1000 annually.  Flood policy is transferable.    The fenced backyard has a dock on the bayou and a fire pit. There is a front porch, a deck on the side and one on the back. It would be a great place to sit and enjoy the beautiful outdoors.  There is plenty of room in the side yard to enjoy outdoor games.  Enjoy all the city of Westlake has to offer; the National Golf Club, The Max restaurant, Horseshoe Casino, Ward 4 Recreation Center, Pinederosa Park Recreation Complex with the under construction waterpark and several ball fields.  Westlake residents receive free membership to the Recreation Center.  Schedule a showing today!
